Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Filling in the distance between hate and love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deductions and suspense of two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, we're on the set of a drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The members of the cast are human too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Detective Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage, far away from human habitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this western-style house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mystery in which love and hatred entwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point of the case is color.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unconsciously chosen every time a person shops...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their own favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, even at the scene of a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let us meet again at the end of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has been Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san, it was perfectly OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though that last wink might have been a little much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:49.50,Top,,0,0,0,,THE UNSEEN SUSPECT\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really saved us on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The big-name actor who always does the opening prologue for this program...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He caught a cold, so we got thrown for a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, please call me in to pinch-hit anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'm also willing to appear in this mystery drama as a special guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, Detective-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, in the story this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the widow that serves as the head of the household, her bitchy daughter, the decrepit butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:31.71,Top,,0,0,0,,Kazami Yoshiki (28)\NRole of the Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, aside from the daughter's murdered husband and my role as a detective, no one beyond those five appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about "bitchy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She isn't bitchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.05,Top,,0,0,0,,Namihara Kasumi (26)\NRole of the Daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's just established as a character who likes to be flashy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's bitchy because you're playing the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Kazami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:52.10,Top,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira (60)\NRole of the Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding the "decrepit" part, could you stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only just turned 60, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your acting that I consider decrepit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I hear you may have been a famous actor ages ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.41,Top,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Nobuharu (31)\NRole of the Daughter's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's not quarrel before filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.04,Top,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Nobuharu (31)\NRole of the Daughter's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazami-kun, you keep your cool too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, Ujou-san's late, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, by Ujou-san, do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The former number one refreshing actress, Ujou Ruri-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're gonna meet Ujou-san too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the one who nominated you as our stand-in on the prologue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know about being the former number one refreshing whatever, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not by that old spinster lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I would refuse it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a washed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.21,Top,,0,0,0,,Ujou Ruri (37)\NRole of the Female Head of Household
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urine-smelling little boy like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's really her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's even prettier in person than on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri Kogorou, it's nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it seems it was you who requested me for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not the first time, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after seeing this beauty spot under my lips, you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beauty spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doigaki Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Ruri-ppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been such a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since middle school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way... They're acquaintances...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not with this new surname!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, back then, you wore those coke-bottle glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I become a fine woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You certainly did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how come Ruri-ppe isn't married?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beauty like you could have anyone you wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I've always been head-over-heels for you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, please stop joking—he'll take you seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that child is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, just some kid from the neighborhood, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his daughter, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're Eri-chan's-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we were together from kindergarten all the way to middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's still a mystery, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the school's most talented girl, Eri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the school's naughtiest boy, Kogorou-chan, were so much in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That they even got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were in love for that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Eri-chan, who was always cool toward others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would get really upset when the opponent was Kogorou-chan and rush at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why everyone around would make fun of them and say, "The lovers' quarrel has started again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still going at it even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the vulgar Kogorou-chan is now a renowned detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Scene 134, camera rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body in front of the fireplace is covered by a gray tablecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hanging on the chair from this table...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the victim's black coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, found next to the body after rolling there, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon that was used to bludgeon the victim to death:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A golf club with a white cover attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I've already solved the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of airs are you putting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we were really doing it, I'd reveal the trick at this point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, those lines aren't in the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight, Detective Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might I have you solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, why did the culprit cover the body with a tablecloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the culprit loved the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they thought that just leaving the body like that would be hard to endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's a coat hung on the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did they go to the trouble of using the tablecloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, the reason for that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the gray tablecloth seemed warmer than the black coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you're not saying that's your answer, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say the hint in the prologue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, why would gray seem warmer than black?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even your friends didn't amount to much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, do it seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, spit out the truth, Kogorou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible, impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For this degree of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so simple a deduction that, against my better judgment, I acted as if it were difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point is, it wasn't that the culprit wanted to cover the body with the tablecloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But rather that the culprit didn't want to cover the body with the black coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since black is their favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit subconsciously believed that utilizing items of their favorite color...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would unintentionally draw suspicion towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, take a close look at the golf bag propped against the fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the head of the club with the black cover has been caught and is sticking out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is evidence that the culprit was going to use the club with the black cover as the weapon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the middle of pulling it out, stopped and switched to white.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if you recognize the fact that this room's furniture and curtains are uniformly black...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this being due to the tastes of the head of the household...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is the one that's even wearing a black dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe, the female head of the household that you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Sleeping Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You decisively hit the mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as the rumors say, right, Kogorou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, it would've been better if you'd just taken it seriously from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, the real thing is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A corpse doesn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Nobuharu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasumi, did you switch to this guy as the next one after that scriptwriter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad—I guess that's still off the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't shape up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old man, is it really smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To say something like that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know all about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your secret meetings every night with your young lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who that woman is or where she's from I don't know for certain yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already got a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pretty damn good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with those faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's how it is, I don't care if this program fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be sleeping in the back room until the heat dies down, so just film scenes I don't appear in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the son of the main sponsor for-this program, a newspaper company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why he knows all kinds of secret information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between the bad terms of the contract and that delinquent character becoming popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're taking in quite a sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I didn't want to appear in a program with that guy as the star either, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An order came down from the agency telling me to appear due to the high ratings, so I reluctantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was able to see Kogorou-chan for the first time in a while, so I guess it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break for 30 minutes and start again after we're all relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had a big quarrel over Worcestershire sauce versus soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad and Mom did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back in elementary school, during the training for Home Economics...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They had a big battle over which to put on top of sunny-side-up fried eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eri-chan said that, because sunny-side-up fried eggs were western food, it should be Worcestershire sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro-chan declared that, for the Japanese people, it should be soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gets less and less understandable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why they got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, when it came time to eat the food that was made...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They ate in exactly the same order, and the whole class had a big laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, they both said, "Stop copying me," and began to quarrel over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, I can't say whether they were right for each other or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough stories from long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, please keep telling more, more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, the weather report did say there was a chance of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we all go outside and see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's only five minutes of the break left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, even if it's only five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first snow of the season!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, it's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snow, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see Ruri-san anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Ruri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought we came out here together, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no good—his pupils are dilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's already dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did this horrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the type to make enemies, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be the case that the first one to discover the body would be the first to be suspected?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it—it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came in here, he was already covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe me, Kogorou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be fooled by her tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An actress' tears are one of the tools of her trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Kasumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if it keeps going like this, we'll end up being the ones suspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Kazami Yoshiki-san, 28 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is exsanguination as a result of damage to his left carotid artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably attacked while sleeping on this sofa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When his neck was sliced with a blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The approximate time of death was between 7:50 PM, when the victim came to this room to take a nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To when his body was discovered at 8:20 PM—an interval of 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we came into this room while touring the house, he was snoring, sound asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just around 8:00, wasn't it, Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Dad looked at his watch and remarked that he had fallen sound asleep within ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-san and Conan-kun, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ohhh, Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you had to look after my little brother the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou-chan, is he an acquaintance of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How very nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Yokomizo from the Shizuoka Prefectural Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great to finally be able to meet you, Mrs. Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:18:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you can say it's wrong, or you can also say it's not so wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's totally wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a just a joke, a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, by some chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the actress, Ujou Ruri-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now that I think about it, you're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the heck's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so many actors and actresses are gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if this is the filming of a drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because... That's exactly what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it was like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this western-style house in the recesses of Mount Fuji, you were filming a mystery drama when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A real murder case occurred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like the story where the mummy hunter himself became the mummy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? In the 20 minutes after 8:00 PM, the time that the murder was thought to have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:19:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had taken a break from filming and all the staff had been in groups of two or more, and thus have alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those without an alibi are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who discovered the body, Ujou Ruri-san, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those who claimed they were alone in their rooms checking lines in the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Namihara Kasumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Nagumo Nobuharu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could only have been one of you four, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Ujou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In detail, tell us the state of the room when you discovered the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the break, along with Kogorou-chan—no, Mouri-san and his group, we were taking a look around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, because snow started falling, we invited the staff to go outside to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the snow was so pretty, I wanted to show it to Kazami-kun, and came to this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazami-kun had become angry and sullen over some things that happened during filming...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when I opened the door, he was bloody and collapsed on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a joke, so I shook his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I finally realized he was dead, I screamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that scream, you three rushed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, for the time being, can we have you four undergo body searches in separate rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite looking everywhere in this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't found the approximately 10-centimeter long blade used to slit Kazami-kun's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, none of the four had anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, we also searched the staff's belongings and thoroughly searched the other rooms, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only items in the kitchen that could have been the weapon were carving knives, a fruit knife, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A box-cutter from inside the staff toolbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no luminol reaction from any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the victim had on him was a pack of cigarettes, a lighter, and his wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still searching the drainage outlets and the area around this house with a metal detector, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been no report that they've found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though we found what we think is the golf glove and the coat that the culprit used during the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't we find the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, since the glove and the coat were both props that were used for the drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one was in the room where they had been left because of the break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that anyone could have taken them easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, where are the four suspects now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're in the room with Mouri-san, awaiting further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the criminal is one of these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Transporting the weapon somewhere far away is impossible in the short time frame of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though that's the ease, why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't the weapon be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:24.05,Top,,0,0,0,,THE UNSEEN SUSPECT\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorou-chan, you smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't, Ruri-ppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, have you forgotten? About my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:44.13,Top,,0,0,0,,Ujou Ruri (37)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, he was pretty famous in the neighborhood for his hatred of smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! As a result, his outlook toward smoking transferred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that makes you the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:57.54,Top,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Nobuharu (31)\NActor - Nagumo Akira's Son
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my mother was the one in my house who disliked smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:02.84,Top,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira (60)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.58,0:23:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even got my father, who had been a heavy smoker...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To quit smoking as soon as I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what do you do for scenes in dramas where you have to smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In those cases, I just hold a cigarette in my lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep—when we're forced to by the director or the producer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, no matter how much time goes by, you'll always be a second-rate actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.23,Top,,0,0,0,,Namihara Kasumi (26)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for a certain someone who sells herself as being a refreshing actress...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be good for her healthy image.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:39.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of me, who can converse with him so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as the murdered Kazami-san said...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that those two are lovers off-screen as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the lover that this person is secretly meeting with...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.43,0:24:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do know who the culprit is yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Great Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mouri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't bother the police, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.84,0:24:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.13,0:24:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are your intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.89,0:24:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding your courtship of her - I'm asking what you're intending to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.81,0:24:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, about Ruri-ppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.48,0:24:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not courting her - we're just childhood friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.65,0:24:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it really just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.73,0:24:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is just that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.61,0:24:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.78,0:24:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you do anything unsightly, I won't forgive you even if you are a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.20,0:25:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.41,0:25:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.67,0:25:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like I've had this feeling before...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.38,0:25:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.42,0:25:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.09,0:25:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little boy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.43,0:25:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This toolbox was left unattended in this room along with the golf gloves and the coat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.81,0:25:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I was thinking that, besides a box-cutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.27,0:25:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There might there be something else in here that could be used for cutting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to play detective, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.94,0:25:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just know the police already searched that toolbox top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.03,0:25:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even this tape measure?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.32,0:25:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.32,0:25:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.58,0:25:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spiking a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.54,0:25:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, spiking is...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.25,0:25:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's using sticky tape to mark a place on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.88,0:25:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like where to put set furniture and where the actors should stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.09,0:25:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the filming will probably be canceled, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,: Just in case, I guess I'll remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.30,0:25:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.72,0:25:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something strange about this sticky tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.01,0:26:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bulging a little, and something's stuck at the edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.69,0:26:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.19,0:26:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cotton?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.61,0:26:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, now I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.11,0:26:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the weapon was!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.82,0:26:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason why it hasn't been found!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.99,0:26:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the coat and the gloves having been left here in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.54,0:26:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a simple task to commit the crime in this room 7 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.58,0:26:29.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's left is who did it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.38,0:26:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.59,0:26:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The behavior of Ruri-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.93,0:26:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who saw snow from that window and suddenly compelled everyone to go outside to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.93,0:26:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! It's Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.69,0:26:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That brat, loitering around the scene of the crime again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.36,0:26:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.57,0:26:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.24,0:26:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.95,0:27:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.16,0:27:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Inspector Yokomizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.79,0:27:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went outside a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you all smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.92,0:27:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.88,0:27:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to take another look at the evidence, so can I borrow some gloves from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.14,0:27:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... This is the wallet, these are the cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.60,0:27:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The coat, the gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.77,0:27:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.98,0:27:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.99,0:27:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's out of lighter fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.62,0:27:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've solved the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.33,0:27:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to put Uncle to sleep with this tranquilizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.79,0:27:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.83,0:27:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tranquilizer dart isn't coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.42,0:27:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I used it up during the camera rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.80,0:27:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.09,0:28:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't produce "Sleeping Kogorou" like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.51,0:28:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.93,0:28:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's like this, I'll have to give Uncle a lot of hints.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.39,0:28:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.39,0:28:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed a lot of things, will you hear me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.94,0:28:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it'll help you solve the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.03,0:28:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.82,0:28:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.58,0:28:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Solved the ease?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.96,0:28:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, Mouri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.25,0:28:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.59,0:28:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nowhere really.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.84,0:28:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just walking around this house looking for keys to solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.92,0:28:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.05,0:28:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you solved it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.01,0:28:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mystery of the vanished weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.05,0:28:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, what I found weren't keys, but this brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.10,0:28:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.73,0:28:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.81,0:28:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then well continue the search for the weapon, so if you there's anything you notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.28,0:29:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll let you know right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.74,0:29:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.41,0:29:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only I could use the tranquilizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.62,0:29:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His expression changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.87,0:29:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought, Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.71,0:29:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's figured out the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.46,0:29:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe, I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.97,0:29:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! That person's not the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.85,0:29:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.06,0:29:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have to hit Uncle on the head with something to make him lose consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.85,0:29:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something to kick... Something to kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.61,0:29:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's locked! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.15,0:29:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's locked, I can't go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.78,0:29:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's the matter, Kogorou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.16,0:29:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Locking the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.20,0:29:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you want to seduce me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.04,0:29:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't hear the conversation inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.09,0:30:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The most I can do is throw this transmitter through the gap under the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.51,0:30:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.64,0:30:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think that I'm the culprit who murdered Kazami-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.93,0:30:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And want to persuade me to turn myself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.06,0:30:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.36,0:30:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I definitely want to recommend confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.53,0:30:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.32,0:30:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, Uncle's in the wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.95,0:30:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't stop him soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.66,0:30:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I definitely want to recommend confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.21,0:30:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.75,0:30:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, Uncle's in the wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.34,0:30:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I don't stop him soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.67,0:30:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the one I want to confess isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.59,0:30:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the one you're covering for...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.43,0:30:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.60,0:30:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Kogorou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.15,0:31:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I have to protect Nagumo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.23,0:31:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.65,0:31:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right before you noticed the falling snow outside the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.24,0:31:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.57,0:31:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the staff in the room next to the window opened the door and came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should have been reflected in the glass embedded in that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.08,0:31:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The figure of Nagumo-san, who had just come out of the next room where Kazami-san had been taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.55,0:31:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The figure of the murderer who was about to leave the room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.18,0:31:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upon noticing the staff, was surprised and shut himself back into the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.64,0:31:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging by that behavior, you suspected that he may have perpetrated some sort of act...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.81,0:31:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by telling everyone to go outside to see the snow, you made sure no one went near that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.70,0:31:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed that just a little while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.99,0:31:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Conan was by the door of the crime scene, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.91,0:31:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found him before turning the corner of the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:32:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was reflected in the glass of that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.08,0:32:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy was.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.79,0:32:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"As expected of the great detective," is what I'd like to say at this point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.01,0:32:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon hasn't been found yet, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.22,0:32:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blade that sliced through the napping Kazami-kun's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.02,0:32:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than the imaginary story that says I witnessed the murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.52,0:32:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you first solve the mystery of the disappearing 10-centimeter long blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.44,0:32:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been so fixated on searching for a 10-centimeter long blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.66,0:32:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likely because no one considered that it could have been transformed into a 2-centimeter long lump of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the box-cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.71,0:32:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After murdering Kazami-san, the culprit broke the blade into small pieces, and hid the collected ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.30,0:32:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the lighter that Kazami-san was carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.14,0:32:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You got it, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.23,0:33:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Kogorou-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.98,0:33:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if bloody box-cutter blades are found inside that lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.48,0:33:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't necessarily mean that the weapon has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.94,0:33:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blade had to be 10 centimeters long in order to be able to cut so deeply into the neck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.20,0:33:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the blades aren't properly inserted into the box-cutter's grip, it wouldn't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.54,0:33:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as for that grip, shouldn't blood have spurted onto it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.79,0:33:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, they should have found a box-cutter grip that reacted to the luminol!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, come on Uncle! Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.39,0:33:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.47,0:33:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.72,0:33:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First you'd have to find the grip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.81,0:33:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.60,0:33:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.44,0:33:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.65,0:33:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.57,0:33:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right... Say, Ran-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.32,0:33:56.62,Top,,0,0,0,,Translator's Note: "Gamu teepu" means sticky tape. Conan is quoting the word "Gum," which in Japanese generally calls for the particle "te" after the quoted word or phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.32,0:33:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Gum"-te! Do you have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.70,0:33:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gum... Te?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.62,0:34:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as anti-drowsiness gum, I think I brought it since Dad asked me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.75,0:34:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.00,0:34:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(gamu teepu)\NIt's sticky tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.17,0:34:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the box-cutter were wrapped with sticky tape from the grip to the end of the blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.13,0:34:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be possible to avoid having blood spurt onto the grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.51,0:34:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the crime, he peeled off the blood-covered tape, and probably stuck it to the floor on the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.56,0:34:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, on that floor, there are sticky-tape markings everywhere which made it difficult to take note of!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.19,0:34:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.73,0:34:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why does that mean it had to be Nagumo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.03,0:34:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that kind of trick, I could have done it because I was the first to find the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.82,0:34:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the snow as a distraction, I could use the opportunity to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.58,0:34:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's stupid! That you would kill anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.50,0:34:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, how stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.87,0:34:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Conan-kun, it looks like the gum is inside the rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.42,0:34:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Ran-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.76,0:34:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you put on a brassiere?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.09,0:34:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, I've never used one, so I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.72,0:35:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here! Boys don't need to know that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.02,0:35:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.23,0:35:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.98,0:35:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This crime is impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.11,0:35:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.11,0:35:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.57,0:35:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you hide the box-cutter blades in this lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.53,0:35:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, inside the cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything under the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.29,0:35:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Kogorou-chan's deduction must be wrong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.50,0:35:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your saying that Nagumo-san is the culprit must be wrong too!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.30,0:35:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri-ppe...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This type of lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.72,0:35:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the kind where you add the lighter fluid onto the cotton that's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.26,0:35:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, without first removing the bottom, and then taking out the cotton that's inside to make space...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.40,0:35:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blades of the box-cutter cannot be hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.02,0:35:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a smoker...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.61,0:35:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw that the lighter wouldn't light, I realized that meant the cotton had been removed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.49,0:36:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for you, a person who hates smoking and has never used a lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.03,0:36:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd never think that something could be hidden there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.04,0:36:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we consider that this person would not only think of that, but would also be someone you'd want to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.46,0:36:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could only be the ex-heavy smoker Nagumo Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.01,0:36:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I said it earlier, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.09,0:36:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I want to protect Nagumo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.30,0:36:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I meet him every now and then for work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.81,0:36:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We aren't that dose...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.64,0:36:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.06,0:36:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's your...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lover, lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.48,0:36:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Real father, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.95,0:36:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.33,0:36:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't a single item used during the crime that was prepared in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.04,0:36:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, it was a haphazard crime that was thought up on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.75,0:37:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cotton, heavy with the scent of the lighter fluid, was probably covered up by the sticky tape on the set, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.55,0:37:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would probably be found as soon as someone looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.51,0:37:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After committing the crime, in a situation where anyone could have come in at any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.31,0:37:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking the cotton out from the lighter and putting the box-cutter blades inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.81,0:37:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be impossible to do while still wearing gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.07,0:37:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a certainty that fingerprints would have been left somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.99,0:37:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, before the evidence becomes known, have your father turn himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.54,0:37:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Kogorou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.91,0:37:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo Akira is my real father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.92,0:37:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was conceived during the time that he and my mother were both members of a failing theater troupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.26,0:37:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though my mother was pregnant, she didn't realize it until after she had broken up with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.55,0:37:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And had started dating the man that you, Kogorou-chan, knew as my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was something I never would have imagined in my wildest dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.27,0:38:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I co-starred with him, and he said that I looked just like his own mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.95,0:38:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked my mother for the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.57,0:38:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had called asking to meet with me, so I went to complain to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.04,0:38:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, "It's too late for you to play the role of my father."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.54,0:38:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.04,0:38:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right in front of me, he broke down and cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.67,0:38:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I met with him every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.13,0:38:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, a father is always a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.89,0:38:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His killing of Kazami-kun was for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.98,0:38:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was known that he was my real father, it would be a big mess for my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.86,0:38:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.36,0:38:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, Kogorou-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.70,0:38:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a big favor to a childhood friend, can you keep his crime to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.37,0:38:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.25,0:38:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.54,0:39:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that sort of deal, especially since it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.63,0:39:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I wouldn't want my childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.68,0:39:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be bound by such a heartbreaking, sorrowful lie for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.81,0:39:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought so, Kogorou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.61,0:39:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That part of you hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.44,0:39:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.57,0:39:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called you over himself and told you the truth about our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.66,0:39:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, at that time, he didn't say anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.04,0:39:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how did you know we were father and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.25,0:39:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I realized it from Nagumo-san's manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.46,0:39:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that of a man facing down a rival who was courting his lover, but instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.47,0:39:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same feeling I had picked up on when I went to meet Eri's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.55,0:39:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a father's worry for his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.69,0:40:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, as expected, it's Eri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.77,0:40:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm no match for her, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.11,0:40:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't Eri, it was her stubborn father that I was reminded of...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.70,0:40:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.57,0:40:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During middle school, the reason why I studied extra hard to the point where I had to wear glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.87,0:40:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was because I wanted to catch a certain someone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.79,0:40:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was certain that you liked smart girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.46,0:40:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.55,0:40:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result of her persuasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.76,0:40:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagumo-san turned himself in...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.22,0:40:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this real-life mystery drama came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.77,0:42:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? You met Ruri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.11,0:42:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was surely even more beautiful than she seems on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.20,0:42:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.74,0:42:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That she was the actress Ujou Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.41,0:42:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.08,0:42:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, unlike that person, I went to the class reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.75,0:42:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, I heard all kinds of things from Ujou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.13,0:42:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like how Mom and Dad had a big quarrel over soy sauce and Worcestershire sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.59,0:42:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was because he always puts Worcestershire sauce on sunny-side-up fried eggs when he's alone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.35,0:42:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he's with me, he gets embarrassed and forces himself to use soy sauce - it really bugged me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.98,0:42:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.27,0:42:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, Dad does always put Worcestershire sauce on his sunny-side-up fried eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.11,0:42:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just that dense of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.07,0:42:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.82,0:42:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing from so long ago, I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.37,0:43:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, these gloves - which do you think are better?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.75,0:43:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.33,0:43:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I think I'd go with the black ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.59,0:43:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think these gray ones seem better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.75,0:43:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.30,0:43:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because gray is written "mouse color"!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.09,0:43:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A color with an animal's name in it, doesn't it seem like it'd be warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.43,0:43:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the gray tablecloth seemed warmer than the black coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.65,0:43:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did I say something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.90,0:43:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.40,0:43:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.95,0:43:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You strange child...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.09,0:43:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a strange old man...
